Mrs. James HOWARD, Appellant, v. L. R. POWELL, Jr., and Henry W. Anderson, Receivers of Seaboard Air Line Railway, Appellees. No. 11730. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Oct. 30, 1946. J. N. Peacock, Jr., of Albany, Ga., and Frank S. Twitty, of Camilla, Ga., for appellant. A. B. Conger, of Bainbridge, Ga., for appellees.

Before HOLMES, WALLER, and LEE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the Court below is affirmed.
